apt-deploy (13.04) precise; urgency=low

  * Fixed root logon
  * will now always log in as root to remote systems
  * Will now look for host-list.conf in /etc/apt-deploy if none is
    specified with -f switch.   Will now execute apt-get as super user.
  * Added ability to parse host list file.  Added function to execute
    apt-get command on remote system using stdin.
  * Testing file parsing. DO NOT USE
  * Initial debianization

 -- Paul Robichaud <paul@paulrobichaud.com>  Sat, 06 Apr 2013 20:33:12 -0500

apt-deploy (0.1-public1) precise; urgency=low

  * Initial release.

